<title>INDIA: FORECAST - Bombay 30-share index 96/97 1st half consensus.</title>
<headline>FORECAST - Bombay 30-share index 96/97 1st half consensus.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1996-10-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Following are the projections of 14 leading securities houses polled by Reuters, on September 24, on their expectations for the first half 1996/97 (April-March) results of 30 top Indian stocks which make up the benchmark Bombay index.</p>
